## Description
`DatabaseHelper.java` uses a lazy singleton pattern without synchronization:

```java
private static Connection connection = null;
public static Connection getConnection() {
    if (connection == null) {
        connection = DriverManager.getConnection(...);
    }
    return connection;
}
```

## Impact
- Race condition: multiple threads can create multiple connections
- Shared connection across threads without synchronization
- Connection may be closed by one thread while another is using it

## Files Affected
- `src/main/java/com/taskflow/util/DatabaseHelper.java`
